'''Marcos Álvarez Pérez'''  is a [[Mexican people|Mexican]] politician affiliated with the [[Party of the Democratic Revolution]]. As of 2014 he served as Deputy of the [[LIX Legislature of the Mexican Congress]] representing the [[State of Mexico]] as replacement of [[Héctor Miguel Bautista López]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Perfil del legislador|url=http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Librerias/pp_PerfilLegislador.php?SID=&Referencia=1707869|publisher=Legislative Information System|accessdate=28 April 2014}}</ref>

